| **********************
| * ZapPMS - Tim Tyler *
| **********************

mode_pms
Tim Tyler's colouring mode for PMS files.
For more details there is a help file available.

PMS_FLAGSTOGGLE <word> (ZapPMS Tim Tyler)
This has the same syntax as the WFORMAT_TOGGLE command.  It ticks menu
entries if it is attached to them.

PMS_SETDELAY <byte> (ZapPMS Tim Tyler)
Sets the delay in centiseconds used by bracket matching.

PMS_SETINDENT <byte> (ZapPMS Tim Tyler)
A useless command - sets the size of the indentation in characters used.
